# =============================================================================
# BOT & AGENT TOKEN MAPPING
# =============================================================================
# GITLAB_BOT_TS_TOKEN      -> @bot-typescript-local  (TypeScript code)
# GITLAB_BOT_OSSA_TOKEN    -> @bot-ossa-local        (OSSA validation)
# GITLAB_BOT_CI_TOKEN      -> @bot-ci-local          (CI/CD pipelines)
# GITLAB_BOT_DEV_TOKEN     -> @bot-native-local      (General dev)
# GITLAB_BOT_WIKI_TOKEN    -> @bot-wiki-aggregator   (Documentation sync)
#
# K8s Agents (GitOps deployments):
# AGENT_K8_TS_LOCAL        -> TypeScript local namespace
# AGENT_K8_TS_PROD         -> TypeScript production namespace
# AGENT_K8_GITLAB_LIB_CI   -> GitLab components CI
# AGENT_K8_INFRA_PROD      -> Infrastructure production
